Test Name	What It Checks	Key Metrics
Performance Testing	Speed & resource usage	Inference time, Memory, CPU/GPU load
Consistency Testing	Stable, repeatable outputs	Deterministic outputs, Variance
Accuracy Testing	Expected structured output	Pass/Fail rate, Semantic similarity
Completeness Testing	No missing fields	Missing elements count
Robustness Testing	Handles different input variations	Handles short/long/noisy inputs
Hallucination Testing	No extra/unverified information	Hallucination score
Regression Stability	No unintended model regressions	Unexpected format changes